@DocumentManagementSystem.AIService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5281

### Query the mock AI service (JSON response)
POST {{DocumentManagementSystem.AIService_HostAddress}}/api/ai/query
Content-Type: application/json
X-Roles: ai.query

{
  "prompt": "Summarize the latest workflow activity.",
  "contextId": "demo-workflow",
  "contextLabel": "Invoice approval",
  "stream": false
}

### Stream a mock AI response using server-sent events
POST {{DocumentManagementSystem.AIService_HostAddress}}/api/ai/query
Accept: text/event-stream
Content-Type: application/json
X-Roles: ai.query

{
  "prompt": "List the next steps for the approval queue.",
  "stream": true
}
